Gun Sales and Gun Violence Events

Data Information

These graphs show gun sales and gun violence events across the United States for the last several years. The data is updated weekly

Data is from the NICS background check database linked on the Buzzfeed github repository. Gun violence events are available and updated regularly at gunviolence.org, please check out their site for more information. Mass shootings include events with 4 or greater persons involved.
